42
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,680
Wow, what do you put our chances at?

43
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,200
Zero percent.

44
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,120
Unless we perform an immediate

45
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,640
emergency morale transplant stat.

46
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,200
Oh, sounds risky.

47
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:08,600
Don't worry, there is a surefire cure.

48
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:09,760
Employee of the month.

49
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:12,680
Every awesome place I've worked had one.

50
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:16,240
Bear Stearns, Lehman Brothers, AIG,

51
