65
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,600
For what?

66
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,440
Nip slip.

67
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:43,320
Oh, okay.

68
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,880
I don't know how those get on there.

69
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:45,720
Well.

70
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:46,800
