128
00:04:27,260 --> 00:04:28,100
Was she?

129
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:29,440
I didn't see it either, but one has to assume.

130
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,280
Huh?

131
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,120
Oh yeah, I guess so.

132
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:31,940
Okay.

133
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:32,780
Whoa!

134
