I love having Pam around.

135
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,820
I don't know what I'd do without her.

136
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:40,880
Whenever Erin shows me her work, I just say, looks great.

137
00:04:41,740 --> 00:04:43,400
Looks great.

138
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,240
Looks great.

139
